This is a CD image file. You should be able to either burn it with your favorite software, or find a BIN to MPG/AVI converter.

To work with daemon tools you need to rename -Introduction to Digital Painting in Adobe Photoshop.bin- file to -Gnomon_Workshop .bin- (Be aware that there's a space bar between word Workshop and coma(.))
Good luck!!!
